# SecPostureIQ — Trivy vulnerability ignore list
#
# Only add CVEs here when they are confirmed as non-exploitable in our
# deployment context. Each entry must include a justification.

# CVE-2025-15558: docker/cli privilege escalation via malicious plugin binaries
# Severity: HIGH | Affects: github.com/docker/cli (bundled in gh CLI binary)
# Justification: This is a Windows-only vulnerability (malicious DLL sideloading).
# Our container runs on Linux (python:3.11-slim). The gh binary is used only for
# Copilot SDK runtime communication, not for Docker operations.
# Will be resolved when GitHub CLI releases a version with docker/cli >= 29.2.0.
CVE-2025-15558
